Mom user docs:

When creating any type of project (collection, sheet, etc) the "thumbnail" for 
    the first "project" will be used as the thumbnail for that projects page. For
    a collection of projects, choose a thumbnail that represents the collection.

To edit a page:
    Click on the gear in the top left of the screen.
    'Composer' will open.
    There are fields all inputs on the page.
    Click 'Save' to preview changes.
    Click "Publish" when you are ready to update the live site.

To add images into the project description:
    Add image.
    Click on the 'edit' button in the center of the image.


